reviewText: Love this album from the end of sixties
This DVD is defective and won't play. This is the second time I ordered this DVD and neither of them worked on any of three DVD players. I think they will not play on American based equipment.
I couldn't watch this dvd because it wouldn't play in my player. It was made for another country. I guess I need to check closer when ordering. I just assumed that they were for usa viewing
